### Variables
@apiVersion = /api/admin
@userId = 1

###
### ============================================
### USER ENDPOINTS - DELETE USER (SOFT DELETE)
### ============================================
###

### Delete User - Success (Super Admin or Admin)
# @name deleteUser
DELETE {{bevalk_base_url}}{{apiVersion}}/users/{{userId}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Delete User - Unauthorized (Secretary Role)
# Should return 403 Forbidden
# Note: Requires a token from a user with secretary role
DELETE {{bevalk_base_url}}{{apiVersion}}/users/{{userId}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{secretaryToken}}

### Delete User - Without Authentication
# Should return 401 Unauthorized
DELETE {{bevalk_base_url}}{{apiVersion}}/users/{{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### Delete User - Not Found
# Should return 404 Not Found if user doesn't exist
DELETE {{bevalk_base_url}}{{apiVersion}}/users/99999
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

